Today's work
Drupal is a free and open-source Content Management System (CMS) used to create websites and web applications.
It is written in PHP and is specially known for building secure, flexible, and powerful websites.

Drupal is used for:

School and college websites

Government portals

Business websites

E-commerce websites

Blogs and news portals
